{"id": "1432054219166191673", "channel_id": "1432054219166191673", "type": 0, "author_id": "210382767295430656", "author_name": "exaegrum", "author_bot": false, "content": "There are a few minor suggestions that I think would make the interface easier to use for keepers.\n\n1) In the sort feature of the Awakener and Wheel of Destiny Inventory page, sorting by enlightenment would be convenient\n2) For a party in the lineup, it would be nice to have a Clear button to instantly remove all awakeners, wheels/covenants, and posse.\n3) Details for banners show 'Current status' for things like 'consecutive non rate-up awakeners or WoD'. A status for 'pity count/consecutive non-SSR' would be a good addition.", "timestamp": "2025-10-26T17:12:12.130000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 5}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1432054219166191673", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「Processing」Quality of Life Features", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
